1. *Rešio* sam da danas odem u šetnju. (I've decided to go for a walk today.)
2. On je već *rešio* taj problem. (He has already solved that problem.)
3. Moramo *rešiti* taj problem što pre. (We need to solve that problem as soon as possible.)
4. Kada budeš *rešavao* taj test, obrati pažnju na uputstva. (When you solve that test, pay attention to the instructions.)
5. Nisam još *rešio* šta ću raditi ovog leta. (I haven't decided yet what I will do this summer.)
6. Oni su *rešeni* da uspeju u svom poslu. (They are determined to succeed in their business.)
7. Kako si *rešio* ovaj matematički problem? (How did you solve this math problem?)
8. Sada kada je problem *rešen*, možemo da idemo dalje. (Now that the problem is solved, we can move on.)
9. *Rešenje* ovog problema zahteva kreativnost i upornost. (The solution to this problem requires creativity and perseverance.)
10. Oni su *rešili* da se venčaju sledeće godine. (They have decided to get married next year.)